{"word":"G3385 - μήτι - mḗti - may'-tee - Not","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μήτι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mḗti</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">may'-tee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Not</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"கேள்வியிலே பதிலிருக்கும் - வினையிடைச் சொல்"},{"paragraph":"whether at all"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3361 - μή - mḗ - may/3361\">G3361</a> and the neuter of <a href=\"#/G5100 - τὶς - tìs - tis/5100\">G5100</a>; <i>whether at all</i>: - not [the particle usually not expressed, except by the form of the question].</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}